snippet.title: Believing Bruce
snippet.description:
Welcome one and all! My name is Believingbruce (it's not really, just in case you wanted to know!)

I'm passionate about helping people, from all over the world, to be more in control of their thoughts+feelings through my #Think #Feel + #Act approach. 

The more I learn, the more I realise what I don't know, so I just LOVE listening to others. #AroundTheCampFire

I appreciate all things human, with a great curiosity for how we connect with ourselves and each other. #InnerVoice. I am also one of the UK’s leading voices on raising awareness of how mental health and wellbeing is at the CORE of human performance #FamilyExperience 

I travel all over the world  helping my global corporate clients, and my Youtube channel is my voluntary offering of bringing some of my knowledge to a wider audience who may not have access to this type of 'self support' type information. 

Be Kind To Yourself, AND Each Other. 😊
